				"&esetAssemblyMode(&abool &9assemblyMode&e)&f - Toggles whether the station is in \"assembly\" mode"
				"&eisInAssemblyMode()&r - Returns whether the station is in \"assembly\" mode"
				"&egetStationName()&r - Returns the name of the station"
				"&esetStationName(&astring &9name&e)&f -  Sets the name of the station"
				"&eisTrainPresent()&r - Returns if a train is stopped in the station"
				"&eisTrainImminent()&r - Returns if a train is about to pull into the station"
				"&eisTrainEnroute()&r - Returns if a tain is traveling to the station"
				"&egetTrainName()&r - Gets the name of the train currently stopped in the station"
